title: Worlds Collide Piano Cover

embed.description: I have been working on playing Worlds Collide, the theme song from League of Legends 2015 World Championsip for a while. I recorded this on 12 May and didn't bother to do some editing until 16 May, which is when I should have uploaded it.

body: I was meant to upload this over a week ago, lol. Hope you enjoy.

replies.body:
That's something I can't do.

but FYI .. that song was SO last year ;)
Well, I am very bad at being able to learn songs quickly. Eg: by the time I might be able to play Taliyah, the login screen would have already been changed.
